title: Krisiun - Conquerors of Armageddon (2000)
description:
A beautiful cacophony of Death Metal.  Krisiun is a band you&#039;ll rarely hear of, and there is no reason for that.  If you find elation in demise and sanctity in malevolence, you&#039;ll enjoy this.
